$d_{i,j}$ 表示 $s[0..i-1]$ 与 $p[0..j-1]$ 是否匹配。

- 边界 $d_{0,0}=T$
- 转移
  1. $p_{j-1}=\text{'*'}$ 
     - 忽略：$d_{i, j-2}$
     - 匹配 $s_{i-1}$：$d_{i-1, j} \wedge (s_{i-1}=p_{j-2} \vee p_{j-2}=\text{'.'})$
  2. 匹配 $s_{i-1}$：$d_{i-1, j-1} \wedge (s_{i-1}=p_{j-2} \vee p_{j-2}=\text{'.'})$
- 结果 $d_{|s|, |p|}$

```csharp
public
class Solution
{
    public bool IsMatch(string s, string p)
    {
        bool[,] res = new bool[s.Length + 1, p.Length + 1];
        res[0, 0] = true;
        for (int i = 0; i <= s.Length; i++)
        {
            for (int j = 1; j <= p.Length; j++)
            {
                res[i, j] = (p[j - 1] == '*' && (res[i, j - 2] || (i > 0 && res[i - 1, j] && (s[i - 1] == p[j - 2] || p[j - 2] == '.')))) || (i > 0 && res[i - 1, j - 1] && (s[i - 1] == p[j - 1] || p[j - 1] == '.'));
            }
        }
        return res[s.Length, p.Length];
    }
}
